For the maximising player, it should compare...

Current Move - (Smallest Potential Move)

If this value is greater than or equal to 0, meaning it isn't a negative action for the player to perform the move

/* -------------------------------- */

For the minimising player, it should compare...

(Largest Potential Move) - Current Move

If this value is greater than or equal to 0, meaning it isn't a negative action for the maximising player to perform the move
